00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,800
Science has a clearer story about multimedia learning than social media does.

2
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:07,600
Multimedia learning combines text, images, and sounds.

3
00:00:07,600 --> 00:00:09,600
But how does it work?

4
00:00:09,600 --> 00:00:13,600
Studies show that our brains process visuals faster than text.

5
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:15,200
This means more retention.

6
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:20,000
In fact, combining these elements can boost learning by up to 60%.

7
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:23,200
So, to learn effectively, mix visuals with audio.

8
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:24,800
It’s simple but powerful.

